categories: Category:Cut content from Rogue One: A Star Wars Story

nodes.text: Dray Nevis was an individual who served the Rebel Alliance as a member of Rogue One alongside K-2SO, Jyn Erso, Senna, Lunak, Ria Talla and Jerris Kestal.
Dray Nevis was one of several characters conceived to be a part of the Rogue One team seen in the film Rogue One: A Star Wars Story, but was cut from the final film.
